data.description: *REDUCED!!* Price improvement to reflect the age of the roof.  This stunning 3 bedroom home combines timeless design, modern amenities, and a picturesque setting to create the ultimate haven for discerning homeowners.  As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a lushly landscaped front yard that sets the tone for the beauty that lies within. Step inside to find a spacious floor plan that combines elegance and comfort.  This exquisite home features an expansive living room/dining room combo adorned with a tastefully designed tray ceiling.  The large kitchen features Corian countertops, gas range, ample storage, and a breakfast nook. The family room is an oasis of comfort, boasting a cozy fireplace framed by built-in shelves, creating a perfect spot for relaxation.  The master suite is a true sanctuary, offering a private retreat complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom featuring a jetted tub, dual vanities, walk-in shower, and walk-in closet. The outdoor space has an in-ground pool inside the screened-in lanai where you can bask in the Florida sunshine, or sit under the covered portion and enjoy your morning coffee.  Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a beautiful home on 1.71 acres. Schedule a tour today and experience the elegance and comfort that this remarkable property has to offer.
